        "end_offset": 884,
        "start": 190.574,
        "end": 226.476
      },
      {
        "segment": "Thus, the harvest shall be such that many will repeat the third-density cycle.",
        "start_offset": 885,
        "end_offset": 963,
        "start": 228.117,
        "end": 246.678
      },
      {
        "segment": "The energies of your Wanderers, your teachers, and your adepts at this time are all bent upon increasing the harvest.",
